pop up.\"},\"281\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-23\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"Fill in the client's details:\"},\"282\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-24\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"**First Name** (required)\"},\"283\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-25\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"**Last Name**\"},\"284\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-26\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"**Phone Number** (required — select the country code from the dropdown)\"},\"285\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-27\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"**Email**\"},\"286\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-28\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"**Date of Birth**\"},\"287\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-29\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"**Notes** — any internal notes about the client\"},\"288\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-30\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"**Location** — assign them to a specific branch\"},\"289\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-31\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"Click **Save Client**. They'll appear in the list and be available for booking straight away.\"},\"290\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-32\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#adding-a-new-client\",\"content\":\"You can also add a client on the spot while booking an appointment in the Calendar — no need to come here first.\"},\"291\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-33\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Click on any client's name to open their full profile in a panel. The profile has three sections:\"},\"292\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-34\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"**Left — Client details**\"},\"293\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-35\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Name, phone, and email\"},\"294\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-36\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"**Edit client** — update any of their details\"},\"295\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-37\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"**Add review** — leave an internal note or review about this client\"},\"296\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-38\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Date of birth (can be added here if not set)\"},\"297\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-39\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Date the client was added to the system\"},\"298\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-40\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"**Middle — Navigation tabs**\\nSwitch between different parts of the client's history:\"},\"299\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-41\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Tab\"},\"300\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-42\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"What it shows\"},\"301\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-43\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Appointments\"},\"302\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-44\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"All appointments with status (Paid, Scheduled, No Show, etc.)\"},\"303\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-45\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Sales\"},\"304\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-46\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"All completed sales with service name, total, and View Details\"},\"305\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-47\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Products\"},\"306\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-48\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Products purchased by this client\"},\"307\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-49\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Vouchers\"},\"308\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-50\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Vouchers linked to this client\"},\"309\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-51\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Memberships\"},\"310\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-52\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Active and completed membership packages with session counts\"},\"311\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-53\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Loyalty\"},\"312\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-54\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"Loyalty programme activity\"},\"313\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-55\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#viewing-a-clients-profile\",\"content\":\"**Right — Detail view**\\nClicking any item in the tabs shows the full detail. For example, clicking a sale opens the VAT invoice with the service, staff, subtotal, VAT, and total — with options to print or void the sale.\"},\"314\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-56\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Feature\"},\"315\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-57\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Details\"},\"316\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-58\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Search\"},\"317\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-59\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"By name, email, or phone\"},\"318\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-60\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Add client form\"},\"319\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-61\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"First name, phone required — email, DOB, notes, location optional\"},\"320\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-62\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Sales total\"},\"321\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-63\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Shown directly in the client list\"},\"322\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-64\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Full profile\"},\"323\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-65\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Appointments, Sales, Products, Vouchers, Memberships, Loyalty\"},\"324\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-66\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Quick add\"},\"325\":{\"id\":\"/docs/clients-67\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/clients\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/clients#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Create a client directly from the Calendar while booking\"},\"326\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"type\":\"page\",\"content\":\"Commission\",\"breadcrumbs\":[\"Docs\"],\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/commission\"},\"327\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-0\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission\",\"content\":\"Set up commission rules for your staff and generate detailed salary slips\"},\"328\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-1\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/commission#team-member-commissions\",\"content\":\"Team Member Commissions\"},\"329\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-2\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Setting up a commission rule\"},\"330\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-3\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Commission Calculations\"},\"331\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-4\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Salary Slip\"},\"332\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-5\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Quick reference\"},\"333\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-6\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission\",\"content\":\"The Commission page is where you define how much each staff member earns from the services they perform, and view a live breakdown of what they've earned. NxCut calculates everything automatically based on real sales data.\"},\"334\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-7\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission\",\"content\":\"Click **Commission** in the left menu to get started.\"},\"335\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-8\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission\",\"content\":\"Commission is only accessible to admin users.\"},\"336\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-9\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission\",\"content\":\"The page is split into two sections: **Team Member Commissions** (your commission rules) and **Commission Calculations** (the live earnings breakdown).\"},\"337\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-10\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#team-member-commissions\",\"content\":\"This section lists all the commission rules you've set up. If no rules have been created yet, it will show \\\"No commission settings found — add a commission setting to get started.\\\"\"},\"338\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-11\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Click **+ Add Commission** in the top right. A form will pop up.\"},\"339\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-12\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Select a **Team Member** from the dropdown.\"},\"340\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-13\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"The **Services Commission** section is enabled by default. This means the staff member earns commission on the services they perform.\"},\"341\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-14\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Choose the **Default commission type**:\"},\"342\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-15\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"**Fixed rate** — a set percentage applied to every sale they make\"},\"343\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-16\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Enter the **Default rate** — the percentage they'll earn (e.g., 30%).\"},\"344\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-17\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Set the **Sales period** — how often commission is calculated. The default is **Monthly**. NxCut will show you exactly when the first and following periods will be.\"},\"345\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-18\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Use the **Sample calculation** box to double-check your setup. Enter a sale amount and NxCut will show you the exact commission calculation — including the threshold, commissionable amount, and final payout.\"},\"346\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-19\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"Click **Create Commission** to save.\"},\"347\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-20\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#setting-up-a-commission-rule\",\"content\":\"The sample calculation updates in real time as you type — use it to make sure the numbers look right before saving.\"},\"348\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-21\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Below the commission rules is the **Commission Calculations** table — a live breakdown of what each staff member has earned for the current period.\"},\"349\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-22\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"At the top you'll see four summary cards:\"},\"350\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-23\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Card\"},\"351\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-24\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"What it shows\"},\"352\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-25\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Team Members\"},\"353\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-26\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Number of staff with sales in this period\"},\"354\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-27\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Total Sales\"},\"355\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-28\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Combined revenue across all staff\"},\"356\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-29\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Total Commission\"},\"357\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-30\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Total commission owed to the team\"},\"358\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-31\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Avg Commission %\"},\"359\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-32\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Average commission rate across the team\"},\"360\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-33\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"The table below shows each staff member with:\"},\"361\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-34\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"**Sales Count** — number of sales completed\"},\"362\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-35\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"**Total Sales** — their total revenue\"},\"363\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-36\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"**Commission Type** — their commission setup, or a **No Setup** badge if none has been configured\"},\"364\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-37\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"**Commission Rate** — their percentage\"},\"365\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-38\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"**Commission Amount** — what they've earned\"},\"366\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-39\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"**Actions** — an eye icon to view the breakdown, and a salary slip icon to open their slip\"},\"367\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-40\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Click **Export CSV** to download the full table for payroll processing.\"},\"368\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-41\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Click the salary slip icon next to any team member to open their **Salary Slip**. This is a full payroll breakdown that can be filled in and downloaded.\"},\"369\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-42\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"The slip is headed with your salon's name and labelled as **Payroll Advice**. It shows the staff member's name, their occupancy percentage, free hours, the month, and their title.\"},\"370\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-43\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"**Earnings section**\"},\"371\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-44\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"A table where you can enter values for each earning type:\"},\"372\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-45\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Earning\"},\"373\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-46\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Description\"},\"374\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-47\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Basic Salary\"},\"375\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-48\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Their fixed monthly salary\"},\"376\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-49\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Over Time\"},\"377\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-50\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Overtime hours worked\"},\"378\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-51\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Voucher\"},\"379\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-52\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Commission from voucher sales\"},\"380\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-53\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Allowance\"},\"381\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-54\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Any allowances paid\"},\"382\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-55\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Products\"},\"383\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-56\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Commission from product sales\"},\"384\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-57\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Bonus\"},\"385\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-58\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Any bonus payment\"},\"386\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-59\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"EOS\"},\"387\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-60\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"End of service accrual\"},\"388\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-61\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Target\"},\"389\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-62\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Target-based incentives\"},\"390\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-63\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Each row has editable fields for rate, days, and hours. The **Total Earning** is calculated automatically.\"},\"391\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-64\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"**Deductions section**\"},\"392\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-65\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Enter any amounts to deduct:\"},\"393\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-66\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Deduction\"},\"394\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-67\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Cash advance\"},\"395\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-68\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Additional deduction\"},\"396\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-69\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"The **Total Deduction** and final **Net Salary** are calculated automatically at the bottom.\"},\"397\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-70\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#salary-slip\",\"content\":\"Once the slip is complete, click **Download XLS** to save it as a spreadsheet, or **Close** to exit without saving.\"},\"398\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-71\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Feature\"},\"399\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-72\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Details\"},\"400\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-73\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Commission rules\"},\"401\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-74\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Set per staff member with a fixed rate and sales period\"},\"402\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-75\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Sample calculator\"},\"403\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-76\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Preview the commission payout before saving\"},\"404\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-77\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"No Setup badge\"},\"405\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-78\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Staff member has sales but no commission rule configured\"},\"406\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-79\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Calculations table\"},\"407\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-80\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Live monthly breakdown per staff member\"},\"408\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-81\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Export CSV\"},\"409\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-82\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Download the full calculations for payroll\"},\"410\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-83\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Salary slip\"},\"411\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-84\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Full payroll advice with earnings, deductions, and net salary — downloadable as XLS\"},\"412\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-85\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Access\"},\"413\":{\"id\":\"/docs/commission-86\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/commission\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/commission#quick-reference\",\"content\":\"Admin only\"},\"414\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"page\",\"content\":\"Dashboard\",\"breadcrumbs\":[\"Docs\"],\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard\"},\"415\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-0\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"content\":\"A real-time overview of your salon's performance — revenue, appointments, and top staff\"},\"416\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-1\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#filtering-by-date-range\",\"content\":\"Filtering by Date Range\"},\"417\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-2\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#sales-by-location\",\"content\":\"Sales by Location\"},\"418\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-3\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#payment-methods\",\"content\":\"Payment Methods\"},\"419\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-4\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#recent-sales\",\"content\":\"Recent Sales\"},\"420\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-5\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#upcoming-appointments\",\"content\":\"Upcoming Appointments\"},\"421\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-6\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#appointments-activity\",\"content\":\"Appointments Activity\"},\"422\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-7\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"Today's Next Appointments\"},\"423\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-8\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"Top Services\"},\"424\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-9\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Top Team Members\"},\"425\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-10\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"Commission Calculations\"},\"426\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-11\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"type\":\"heading\",\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#dashboard-overview\",\"content\":\"Dashboard Overview\"},\"427\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-12\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"content\":\"The Dashboard is the first thing you see when you log in as an admin. It gives you a quick, up-to-date picture of how your salon is performing — without having to dig through reports or spreadsheets.\"},\"428\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-13\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"content\":\"The Dashboard is only visible to admin users.\"},\"429\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-14\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#filtering-by-date-range\",\"content\":\"At the top of the Dashboard is the **Filter by Date Range** bar. By default the dashboard shows recent data, but you can narrow it down to any period you want.\"},\"430\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-15\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#filtering-by-date-range\",\"content\":\"Click **Show Calendar** on the right side of the filter bar. A two-month calendar picker will appear.\"},\"431\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-16\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#filtering-by-date-range\",\"content\":\"Click a **start date**, then click an **end date**. The selected range will be highlighted between the two dates.\"},\"432\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-17\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#filtering-by-date-range\",\"content\":\"The entire Dashboard updates automatically to reflect only that period.\"},\"433\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-18\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#filtering-by-date-range\",\"content\":\"Click **Hide Calendar** to close the picker when you're done.\"},\"434\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-19\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#filtering-by-date-range\",\"content\":\"Use the &#x2A;*\\\\<*&#x2A; and &#x2A;*>** arrows on the calendar to navigate to earlier or later months.\"},\"435\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-20\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#sales-by-location\",\"content\":\"A donut chart showing total revenue broken down by location. Below the chart you'll see the grand total and how many locations are currently active.\"},\"436\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-21\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#sales-by-location\",\"content\":\"This gives you an instant feel for which branches are driving the most revenue — especially useful if you run multiple locations.\"},\"437\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-22\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#payment-methods\",\"content\":\"A donut chart right next to Sales by Location, showing how your revenue was collected — broken down by payment method (Cash, Card, Online, Membership, etc.).\"},\"438\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-23\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#payment-methods\",\"content\":\"Below the chart, each payment method is listed with its exact total for the period. Use this to see whether clients prefer paying by card or cash, or to verify totals against your till at the end of the day.\"},\"439\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-24\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#recent-sales\",\"content\":\"**All locations · Last 7 days**\"},\"440\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-25\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#recent-sales\",\"content\":\"A summary card showing:\"},\"441\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-26\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#recent-sales\",\"content\":\"**Total revenue** collected over the last 7 days\"},\"442\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-27\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#recent-sales\",\"content\":\"**Number of appointments** completed\"},\"443\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-28\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#recent-sales\",\"content\":\"**Appointments value** — the combined price of all booked services\"},\"444\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-29\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#recent-sales\",\"content\":\"Below the numbers, a **line chart** tracks revenue and appointment count day by day so you can spot your busiest days and see whether bookings are translating into actual sales.\"},\"445\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-30\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#upcoming-appointments\",\"content\":\"**All locations · Next 7 days**\"},\"446\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-31\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#upcoming-appointments\",\"content\":\"A summary card showing what's on the books:\"},\"447\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-32\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#upcoming-appointments\",\"content\":\"Total appointments booked\"},\"448\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-33\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#upcoming-appointments\",\"content\":\"How many are **confirmed**\"},\"449\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-34\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#upcoming-appointments\",\"content\":\"How many have been **cancelled**\"},\"450\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-35\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#upcoming-appointments\",\"content\":\"A **bar chart** breaks this down day by day — great for spotting gaps in the schedule or flagging a day that has an unusually high cancellation rate.\"},\"451\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-36\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#appointments-activity\",\"content\":\"A live feed of the most recent appointment events across all your locations — new bookings, updates, checkouts, and cancellations. Each entry shows the date, time, service, client (or Walk-In), duration, and which staff member is assigned.\"},\"452\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-37\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#appointments-activity\",\"content\":\"This is your go-to for staying on top of last-minute changes, especially if you're managing more than one location.\"},\"453\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-38\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"A list of the remaining appointments for today, sorted by time. Each entry shows:\"},\"454\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-39\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"The appointment time\"},\"455\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-40\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"The service being performed\"},\"456\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-41\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"The client's name (or Walk-In)\"},\"457\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-42\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"The staff member handling it\"},\"458\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-43\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"The status badge (e.g., **Booked**)\"},\"459\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-44\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#todays-next-appointments\",\"content\":\"Use this for a quick check of what's still to come in the day.\"},\"460\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-45\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"A table showing which services are being booked the most, ranked by volume.\"},\"461\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-46\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"Column\"},\"462\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-47\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"What it shows\"},\"463\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-48\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"Service\"},\"464\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-49\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"The name of the treatment\"},\"465\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-50\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"This month\"},\"466\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-51\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"How many times it was booked this month\"},\"467\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-52\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"Last month\"},\"468\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-53\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"Last month's count for comparison\"},\"469\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-54\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-services\",\"content\":\"Click on any service name to jump straight to that service in your Catalog.\"},\"470\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-55\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"A table ranking your staff by total sales for the selected month. You can search by name and filter by month and year.\"},\"471\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-56\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Column\"},\"472\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-57\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"What it shows\"},\"473\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-58\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Team member\"},\"474\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-59\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Staff member's name\"},\"475\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-60\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"This month\"},\"476\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-61\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Total sales value for the current month\"},\"477\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-62\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Last month\"},\"478\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-63\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Last month's total for comparison\"},\"479\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-64\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Actions\"},\"480\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-65\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"Generate a salary slip for that team member\"},\"481\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-66\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"The **Actions** column has a salary slip icon — click it to open a formatted breakdown of that person's services, commission, and total payout for the period.\"},\"482\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-67\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#top-team-members\",\"content\":\"You can also export the full table using the **CSV**, **Excel**, or **PDF** buttons in the top-right corner.\"},\"483\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-68\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"At the bottom of the Dashboard is the **Commission Calculations** widget. It shows a live summary of what each staff member has earned in commission for the selected month.\"},\"484\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-69\",\"page_id\":\"/docs/dashboard\",\"tags\":[],\"type\":\"text\",\"url\":\"/docs/dashboard#commission-calculations\",\"content\":\"At the top of the widget you'll see four summary numbers:\"},\"485\":{\"id\":\"/docs/dashboard-70\",\"page_id\"