— add an internal note or review about the client\"],[295,\"**Add review** — leave an internal note or review about this client\"],[219,\"**Add Tip**\"],[952,\"**Add to Calendar** and **Print** buttons\"],[566,\"**Admin vs. Staff** — Admin users can access everything. Regular staff only see what they need for their daily work: Calendar, Sales, Clients, Catalog, and Team.\"],[439,\"**All locations · Last 7 days**\"],[445,\"**All locations · Next 7 days**\"],[217,\"**Apply Discount**\"],[223,\"**Apply Voucher**\"],[19,\"**Appointment cards** — each card shows the client name, service, and time range\"],[443,\"**Appointments value** — the combined price of all booked services\"],[45,\"**Arrived**\"],[488,\"**Avg Commission %** — average commission rate across the team\"],[734,\"**Back to Appointment** button — returns to the linked appointment\"],[911,\"**Booking Page** — opens your live client booking page in a new tab\"],[788,\"**Branch Images** — upload up to 4 photos to showcase the branch (shown on the card)\"],[782,\"**Branch Name** (required)\"],[585,\"**Browse by category** using the tabs across the top: All reports · Sales · Finance · Appointments · Team · Clients · Inventory\"],[51,\"**Cancel**\"],[197,\"**Card**\"],[663,\"**Cash movement summary**\\nA breakdown of how payments were collected — showing each payment method (Cash, Online, Card, etc.) and the amount collected through each. Also shows the total **Payments collected** and how much of that was **tips**.\"],[199,\"**Cash**\"],[56,\"**Checkout** — moves the appointment to the payment screen to collect payment\"],[785,\"**City**\"],[687,\"**Columns:** Purchase Date · Client · Membership name · Service · Sessions (used / remaining with a progress bar) · Cost · Status\"],[671,\"**Columns:** Sale ID · Client (name + phone) · Service · Sale Date · Team Member · Unit Price · Quantity · Discount · Total Price\"],[675,\"**Columns:** Sale ID · Payment Date · Client · Team Members · Payment Method · Tips · Status · Amount\"],[683,\"**Columns:** Sale ID · Payment Date · Client · Team Members · Payment Method · Tips · Status · Amount\"],[693,\"**Columns:** Sale ID · Product Name · Category · Brand · Quantity · Unit Price · Total Price · Current Stock · Sale Date · Status\"],[698,\"**Columns:** Sale ID · Tip Amount · Staff Member · Payment Method · Sale Total · Date\"],[365,\"**Commission Amount** — what they've earned\"],[364,\"**Commission Rate** — their percentage\"],[363,\"**Commission Type** — their commission setup, or a **No Setup** badge if none has been configured\"],[164,\"**Complete the audit** — confirm the counts are correct and lock the audit\"],[677,\"**Completed** — the sale went through successfully\"],[784,\"**Country** (with flag selector)\"],[286,\"**Date of Birth**\"],[391,\"**Deductions section**\"],[838,\"**Delete** (red trash icon) — remove them permanently\"],[808,\"**Delete** (red) — permanently remove it\"],[370,\"**Earnings section**\"],[294,\"**Edit client** — update any of their details\"],[704,\"**Edit client** — update their contact details\"],[836,\"**Edit Shift** — set their weekly working hours\"],[807,\"**Edit** — rename the method or change its status\"],[837,\"**Edit** — update their profile details\"],[285,\"**Email**\"],[783,\"**Email**\"],[946,\"**Existing Client** — enters their registered phone number to pull up their profile\"],[605,\"**Export:** CSV, Excel, PDF.\"],[621,\"**Export:** CSV, Excel, PDF.\"],[625,\"**Export:** CSV, Excel, PDF.\"],[629,\"**Export:** CSV, Excel, PDF.\"],[583,\"**Filter by creator** using the All creators dropdown\"],[584,\"**Filter by type** using the All reports dropdown\"],[604,\"**Filters:** Date range, location, team member, client, payment method.\"],[624,\"**Filters:** Date range, location, team member, payment method, transaction type, amount range.\"],[628,\"**Filters:** Date range, location, team member, payment method.\"],[282,\"**First Name** (required)\"],[342,\"**Fixed rate** — a set percentage applied to every sale they make\"],[151,\"**If you click Save Stock Audit before finishing:**\"],[153,\"**If you click the X (close) button before finishing:**\"],[283,\"**Last Name**\"],[292,\"**Left — Client details**\"],[702,\"**Left — Client details**\"],[194,\"**Left — Payment**\\r\\nChoose how the client is paying. The available options are shown as cards:\"],[288,\"**Location** — assign them to a specific branch\"],[201,\"**Membership**\"],[298,\"**Middle — Navigation tabs**\\nSwitch between different parts of the client's history:\"],[708,\"**Middle — Navigation tabs**\\nSwitch between different views of the client's history:\"],[912,\"**My Website** — opens your full salon website\"],[20,\"**Navigation bar at the top** — use **Today*&#x2A;, &#x2A;*\\\\<*&#x2A;, and &#x2A;*>** to move between days, or click the date to jump to a specific day\"],[945,\"**New Client** — enters their details for the first time\"],[49,\"**No Show**\"],[287,\"**Notes** — any internal notes about the client\"],[442,\"**Number of appointments** completed\"],[203,\"**Online**\"],[668,\"**Payment Methods** — how many different payment methods were used\"],[284,\"**Phone Number** (required — select the country code from the dropdown)\"],[786,\"**Phone** (with country code selector)\"],[731,\"**Print icons** — print as thermal receipt or standard A4 invoice\"],[163,\"**Resume editing** — go back and adjust any counts before finalising\"],[723,\"**Right — Detail view**\\nClicking any item in the tabs shows the full detail on the right side. For example, clicking a sale shows the service, time, staff, subtotal, VAT, and total.\"],[313,\"**Right — Detail view**\\nClicking any item in the tabs shows the full detail. For example, clicking a sale opens the VAT invoice with the service, staff, subtotal, VAT, and total — with options to print or void the sale.\"],[208,\"**Right — Order summary**\\r\\nShows the client's name and phone number, the services being charged, and a full summary:\"],[667,\"**Sale Types** — how many different item types were sold\"],[732,\"**Sale-ID** (copyable)\"],[669,\"**Sales → Appointments**\"],[659,\"**Sales → Daily Sales**\"],[685,\"**Sales → Memberships**\"],[681,\"**Sales → Payments**\"],[691,\"**Sales → Products**\"],[673,\"**Sales → Sales**\"],[696,\"**Sales → Tips**\"],[689,\"**Sales → Vouchers**\"],[361,\"**Sales Count** — number of sales completed\"],[155,\"**Save uncounted as 0** — records those products as having zero stock on the shelf. Use this if you genuinely checked and found nothing.\"],[55,\"**Save** — saves any changes you made\"],[24,\"**Search** by name or phone number\"],[582,\"**Search** by report name or description\"],[769,\"**Settings → Branches**\"],[792,\"**Settings → Calendar**\"],[802,\"**Settings → Payment Methods**\"],[810,\"**Settings → Permissions**\"],[205,\"**Split Payment**\"],[221,\"**Split Payment**\"],[729,\"**Staff Information** — assigned staff member and receptionist\"],[230,\"**Standard Invoice (A4)** — a full-page formatted tax invoice\"],[47,\"**Start**\"],[725,\"**Status badge** (e.g., Completed)\"],[664,\"**Summary bar**\\nFour quick-view numbers at the bottom:\"],[156,\"**Sync counted to previous stock** — leaves those products at whatever stock value was already in the system. Use this if you simply didn't get around to counting them and don't want to affect their records.\"],[485,\"**Team Members** — how many staff have sales this period\"],[229,\"**Thermal Receipt (80mm)** — formatted for a POS receipt printer\"],[17,\"**Time slots running down the page** — the interval (15, 30, or 45 min) is set in Settings → Calendar\"],[816,\"**Toggle: Disable Tips in POS**\"],[813,\"**Toggle: Enable Voucher Tips**\"],[819,\"**Toggle: Enforce Mutual Exclusivity**\"],[487,\"**Total Commission** — total commission owed\"],[212,\"**Total due**\"],[441,\"**Total revenue** collected over the last 7 days\"],[486,\"**Total Sales** — combined revenue across all staff\"],[362,\"**Total Sales** — their total revenue\"],[665,\"**Total Sales** — total revenue for the day\"],[666,\"**Total Transactions** — number of completed transactions\"],[662,\"**Transaction summary**\\nA table showing what was sold by item type (e.g., Service, Product), how many were sold, and the net total.\"],[787,\"**TRN** — your Tax Registration Number, printed on invoices\"],[727,\"**VAT Invoice** number and date\"],[733,\"**Void Sale** button — reverses the transaction if an error was made\"],[678,\"**Voided** (red badge) — the sale was reversed after the fact\"],[815,\"*Off by default.*\"],[818,\"*Off by default.*\"],[821,\"*Off by default.*\"],[525,\"<Card title=\\\"Calendar & Bookings\\\" href=\\\"/docs/calendar\\\" description=\\\"Book, reschedule, and manage appointments for your whole team in one view.\\\" />\"],[528,\"<Card title=\\\"Catalog & Inventory\\\" href=\\\"/docs/catalog\\\" description=\\\"Set up your services, products, membership packages, and gift vouchers.\\\" />\"],[526,\"<Card title=\\\"Checkout\\\" href=\\\"/docs/checkout\\\" description=\\\"Collect payment, apply discounts, add tips, and split bills — all in a few clicks.\\\" />\"],[529,\"<Card title=\\\"Clients\\\" href=\\\"/docs/clients\\\" description=\\\"Keep a full record of every client — their visits, memberships, and voucher balances.\\\" />\"],[531,\"<Card title=\\\"Commission\\\" href=\\\"/docs/commission\\\" description=\\\"Automatically calculate how much each team member earns and generate salary slips.\\\" />\"],[524,\"<Card title=\\\"Dashboard\\\" href=\\\"/docs/dashboard\\\" description=\\\"See how your business is doing at a glance — revenue, appointments, and top performers.\\\" />\"],[894,\"<Card title=\\\"Learn more about Fumadocs\\\" href=\\\"https://fumadocs.dev\\\" />\"],[893,\"<Card title=\\\"Learn more about Next.js\\\" href=\\\"https://nextjs.org/docs\\\" />\"],[532,\"<Card title=\\\"Reporting\\\" href=\\\"/docs/reporting\\\" description=\\\"Dig into your numbers — sales trends, payment breakdowns, tips, and more.\\\" />\"],[527,\"<Card title=\\\"Sales Hub\\\" href=\\\"/docs/sales\\\" description=\\\"View your full sales history — payments, memberships, vouchers, tips, and more.\\\" />\"],[533,\"<Card title=\\\"Settings\\\" href=\\\"/docs/settings\\\" description=\\\"Set up your locations, business hours, payment options, and access rules.\\\" />\"],[530,\"<Card title=\\\"Team Management\\\" href=\\\"/docs/team\\\" description=\\\"Add staff, set their working hours, and control what they can access.\\\" />\"],[534,\"<Card title=\\\"Website & Booking Page\\\" href=\\\"/docs/website\\\" description=\\\"Manage your public booking page and let clients book appointments online.\\\" />\"],[450,\"A **bar chart** breaks this down day by day — great for spotting gaps in the schedule or flagging a day that has an unusually high cancellation rate.\"],[779,\"A **pencil icon** to edit the branch\"],[943,\"A **Summary*&#x2A; panel on the right shows the selected service, agent, and total price. The client can also click **+ Add More** to add additional services to the same booking.\"],[942,\"A calendar shows the current month. Days with available slots are marked with a **green underline**. The client clicks a date to see the available time slots for that day, then taps a green slot to reserve it.\"],[603,\"A detailed record of every sale — including the services sold, discounts applied, payment methods used, staff member, and client. Use this when you need to trace a specific transaction or review sales over a period.\"],[154,\"A dialog titled &#x2A;*\\\"Uncounted products remaining\\\"** will appear, asking how you'd like to handle the items you didn't get to. You'll have two choices:\"],[152,\"A dialog will appear telling you how many products still haven't been counted (e.g., \\\"5 products remaining\\\"). The only option here is **Continue** — this sends you back to finish counting before the audit can be saved.\"],[437,\"A donut chart right next to Sales by Location, showing how your revenue was collected — broken down by payment method (Cash, Card, Online, Membership, etc.).\"],[435,\"A donut chart showing total revenue broken down by location. Below the chart you'll see the grand total and how many locations are currently active.\"],[636,\"A formatted, ready-to-share spreadsheet\"],[953,\"A full **Cost Breakdown** showing the service price, any credits applied, and the balance due\"],[670,\"A full list of every appointment-based sale. Use this when you need to look up a specific service, client visit, or check what was charged and whether a discount was applied.\"],[623,\"A full log of every individual payment collected. Use this to verify payment method totals or trace a specific transaction.\"],[949,\"A green **Appointment Confirmed** message\"],[453,\"A list of the remaining appointments for today, sorted by time. Each entry shows:\"],[451,\"A live feed of the most recent appointment events across all your locations — new bookings, updates, checkouts, and cancellations. Each entry shows the date, time, service, client (or Walk-In), duration, and which staff member is assigned.\"],[607,\"A period-by-period breakdown of your sales, payments, and liabilities. Perfect for month-end reviews and accounting.\"],[415,\"A real-time overview of your salon's performance — revenue, appointments, and top staff\"],[692,\"A record of every product sold, with live stock levels.\"],[136,\"A stock audit is how you check that your physical inventory matches what NxCut thinks you have. It's good practice to run one regularly, especially if products are used during services as well as sold.\"],[137,\"A stock audit moves through three stages: **Stock Session → Stock Entry → Stock Review**. Each stage has its own status so you always know where an audit is up to.\"],[446,\"A summary card showing what's on the books:\"],[440,\"A summary card showing:\"],[470,\"A table ranking your staff by total sales for the selected month. You can search by name and filter by month and year.\"],[460,\"A table showing which services are being booked the most, ranked by volume.\"],[371,\"A table where you can enter values for each earning type:\"],[859,\"A team member profile and a login account are two separate things. A team member profile controls how someone appears on the Calendar. A login account controls how they log in to NxCut. Most staff will need both.\"],[950,\"A unique &#x2A;*ORDER #** for reference\"],[601,\"A visual overview of your salon's performance. Shows key metrics, charts, and trends across revenue, appointments, services, and staff — all in one place.\"],[765,\"Accept Tips Online Only\"],[412,\"Access\"],[568,\"Access all your salon reports — sales, finance, and team performance\"],[479,\"Actions\"],[720,\"Active and completed membership packages (shows count badge)\"],[310,\"Active and completed membership packages with session counts\"],[218,\"Add a fixed or percentage discount to the sale\"],[220,\"Add a gratuity for the staff member\"],[318,\"Add client form\"],[823,\"Add staff, set their schedules, and control what they can access\"],[829,\"Adding a login account (Auth User)\"],[260,\"Adding a new client\"],[761,\"Adding a payment method\"],[97,\"Adding a product\"],[94,\"Adding a service\"],[825,\"Adding a team member\"],[395,\"Additional deduction\"],[885,\"Admin access\"],[413,\"Admin only\"],[541,\"Admins only\"],[559,\"Admins only\"],[562,\"Admins only\"],[565,\"Admins only\"],[226,\"After payment is confirmed, the **Sale Receipt** screen appears. The header turns green and shows a **Paid** badge confirming the transaction is complete.\"],[948,\"After submitting, a confirmation screen appears showing:\"],[302,\"All appointments with status (Paid, Scheduled, No Show, etc.)\"],[712,\"All appointments with status badges (Paid, Scheduled, No Show)\"],[304,\"All completed sales with service name, total, and View Details\"],[714,\"All completed sales with service, total, and a View Details button\"],[686,\"All membership packages that have been sold, with live session tracking.\"],[589,\"All reports\"],[630,\"All reports can be exported in:\"],[639,\"All reports use the same date picker with quick presets:\"],[544,\"All staff\"],[547,\"All staff\"],[550,\"All staff\"],[553,\"All staff\"],[556,\"All staff\"],[690,\"All vouchers that have been purchased or redeemed. Search by client name, voucher name, or voucher code. Filter by date range to narrow results.\"],[764,\"Allow Voucher Usage for Tips\"],[380,\"Allowance\"],[494,\"An eye icon to view their breakdown and a salary slip icon to generate their slip\"],[627,\"An overview of all tips received, broken down by staff member. Shows total tips, number of tipped transactions, average tip, and tip percentage for each person.\"],[159,\"An overview of every product that was counted\"],[381,\"Any allowances paid\"],[385,\"Any bonus payment\"],[700,\"Anywhere you see a **client name** shown as a blue link (in Sales Transactions, Payments, etc.), you can click it to open that client's full profile in a panel on the right.\"],[249,\"Apply extras via ··· menu\"],[182,\"Applying discounts, tips, and vouchers\"],[8,\"Appointment card hover\"],[10,\"Appointment statuses\"],[87,\"Appointment statuses\"],[301,\"Appointments\"],[648,\"Appointments\"],[711,\"Appointments\"],[740,\"Appointments\"],[421,\"Appointments Activity\"],[508,\"Appointments Activity\"],[543,\"Appointments and bookings\"],[323,\"Appointments, Sales, Products, Vouchers, Memberships, Loyalty\"],[869,\"Archived members are hidden from the default view.\"],[830,\"Archiving a team member\"],[61,\"Arrived\"],[88,\"Arrived, Start, No Show, Cancel — updated from the edit panel\"],[214,\"At the bottom left of the checkout screen, click the &#x2A;*···** (three dots) button to reveal additional options:\"],[483,\"At the bottom of the Dashboard is the **Commission Calculations** widget. It shows a live summary of what each staff member has earned in commission for the selected month.\"],[54,\"At the bottom of the panel you'll see two buttons:\"],[429,\"At the top of the Dashboard is the **Filter by Date Range** bar. By default the dashboard shows recent data, but you can narrow it down to any period you want.\"],[42,\"At the top of the edit panel you'll see status action buttons:\"],[484,\"At the top of the widget you'll see four summary numbers:\"],[910,\"At the top right of the page you'll find two quick-access buttons:\"],[349,\"At the top you'll see four summary cards:\"],[883,\"Auth users\"],[828,\"Authenticated Users\"],[570,\"Available reports\"],[359,\"Average commission rate across the team\"],[358,\"Avg Commission %\"],[374,\"Basic Salary\"],[489,\"Below that, the table shows each team member with:\"],[438,\"Below the chart, each payment method is listed with its exact total for the period. Use this to see whether clients prefer paying by card or cash, or to verify totals against your till at the end of the day.\"],[348,\"Below the commission rules is the **Commission Calculations** table — a live breakdown of what each staff member has earned for the current period.\"],[444,\"Below the numbers, a **line chart** tracks revenue and appointment count day by day so you can spot your busiest days and see whether bookings are translating into actual sales.\"],[632,\"Best for\"],[737,\"Best used for\"],[11,\"Blocking time off\"],[384,\"Bonus\"],[2,\"Book, view, and manage all your salon appointments in one place\"],[4,\"Booking a new appointment\"],[231,\"Both formats show:\"],[772,\"Branch name and **Active** status badge\"],[771,\"Branch photo\"],[756,\"Branches\"],[564,\"Business configuration\"],[540,\"Business overview and key numbers\"],[43,\"Button\"],[317,\"By name, email, or phone\"],[406,\"Calculations table\"],[542,\"Calendar\"],[758,\"Calendar\"],[1,\"Calendar & Bookings\"],[875,\"Calendar color\"],[67,\"Cancelled\"],[256,\"Cancels and reverses the transaction if needed\"],[52,\"Cancels the appointment\"],[350,\"Card\"],[248,\"Card, Cash, Membership, Online, or Split\"],[892,\"Cards\"],[394,\"Cash advance\"],[551,\"Catalog\"],[91,\"Catalog & Inventory\"],[106,\"Catalog overview\"],[587,\"Category\"],[879,\"Category permissions\"],[178,\"Checkout\"],[189,\"Checkout is how you collect payment after a client's visit. The whole process happens in a panel that slides in from the right — no page navigation needed.\"],[246,\"Checkout panel slides in with services pre-loaded\"],[188,\"Checkout summary\"],[26,\"Choose **Walk-In Customer** if the client isn't registered\"],[247,\"Choose a payment method\"],[608,\"Choose how to group the data:\"],[341,\"Choose the **Default commission type**:\"],[254,\"Choose Thermal (80mm) or Standard Invoice (A4)\"],[776,\"City and country\"],[860,\"Click **+ Add → Add Auth User**. A form will pop up.\"],[840,\"Click **+ Add → Add Team Member**. A form will pop up.\"],[338,\"Click **+ Add Commission** in the top right. A form will pop up.\"],[805,\"Click **+ Add Payment Method**, enter a name, and save. The new method will immediately be available at checkout.\"],[27,\"Click **Add new client** to create a new profile on the spot\"],[849,\"Click **Add Team Member**.\"],[108,\"Click **Catalog** in the left menu to get started. You'll see five tabs at the top: **Services**, **Products**, **Memberships**, **Vouchers**, and **Stock Audit**.\"],[75,\"Click **Checkout** at the bottom of the panel.\"],[264,\"Click **Clients** in the left menu to get started.\"],[334,\"Click **Commission** in the left menu to get started.\"],[346,\"Click **Create Commission** to save.\"],[866,\"Click **Create User**. The account is active immediately.\"],[798,\"Click **Default** on any day to reset it to the default hours\"],[33,\"Click **Done** when you're finished\"],[853,\"Click **Edit Shift** on the team member's card.\"],[850,\"Click **Edit** on any team member card to update their photo, name, calendar color, category permissions, admin status, or location.\"],[367,\"Click **Export CSV** to download the full table for payroll processing.\"],[433,\"Click **Hide Calendar** to close the picker when you're done.\"],[579,\"Click **Reports** in the left menu to get started.\"],[926,\"Click **Save Changes** when done.\"],[289,\"Click **Save Client**. They'll appear in the list and be available for booking straight away.\"],[113,\"Click **Save**.\"],[120,\"Click **Save**.\"],[127,\"Click **Save**.\"],[134,\"Click **Save**.\"],[856,\"Click **Save**.\"],[72,\"Click **Save**. The blocked slot will appear as a distinct card on the calendar.\"],[35,\"Click **Save*&#x2A;. The appointment is created instantly and appears as a card on the calendar. A green &#x2A;*\\\"Appointment created successfully\\\"** notification will confirm it.\"],[430,\"Click **Show Calendar** on the right side of the filter bar. A two-month calendar picker will appear.\"],[148,\"Click **Start** to begin. The audit moves to the **Stock Entry** stage.\"],[833,\"Click **Team** in the left menu to get started. The page is divided into two sections: **Team Members** and **Authenticated Users**.\"],[789,\"Click **Update Branch** to save.\"],[936,\"Click **Upload Image** to add or replace the landing page photo, then click **Save Changes**.\"],[431,\"Click a **start date**, then click an **end date**. The selected range will be highlighted between the two dates.\"],[680,\"Click any **Client name** to open their Client Profile.\"],[679,\"Click any **Sale ID** to open the full Sale Details panel.\"],[245,\"Click Checkout on the appointment\"],[70,\"Click on an empty time slot in a staff member's column and select **Block Time**.\"],[41,\"Click on an existing appointment card to open the **Edit Appointment** panel. It works the same as the booking panel — you can change the client, add or remove services, or update the time or Status.\"],[291,\"Click on any client's name to open their full profile in a panel. The profile has three sections:\"],[469,\"Click on any service name to jump straight to that service in your Catalog.\"],[74,\"Click on the appointment card to open the Edit Appointment panel.\"],[251,\"Click Pay\"],[280,\"Click the **+ Add** button in the top right corner. A form will pop up.\"],[114,\"Click the **Edit** icon on any service to update its details. If you want to stop a service from showing up in bookings without deleting it permanently, just toggle the status to inactive. To remove it entirely, use the **Delete** option.\"],[908,\"Click the **globe icon** in the left menu to manage your website settings.\"],[780,\"Click the **pencil icon** on any branch card to open the Edit Branch form.\"],[228,\"Click the **print icon** (or the document icon for A4) to open the **Invoice Preview**. You'll see two format options:\"],[806,\"Click the &#x2A;*···** (three dots) on any card to reveal two options:\"],[841,\"Click the &#x2A;*+** circle at the top to upload a profile photo (JPEG or PNG, under 2 MB). This is optional but recommended — it helps identify staff on the Calendar.\"],[207,\"Click the option that applies. The selected method will be highlighted.\"],[368,\"Click the salary slip icon next to any team member to open their **Salary Slip**. This is a full payroll breakdown that can be filled in and downloaded.\"],[724,\"Clicking a **Sale ID** or **View Details** anywhere in the Sales Hub opens the full Sale Details panel. This shows:\"],[549,\"Client directory and profiles\"],[268,\"Client name\"],[726,\"Client name and phone\"],[655,\"Client Profile\"],[257,\"Clients\"],[548,\"Clients\"],[891,\"Code Block\"],[179,\"Collect payment, print receipts, and manage completed sales\"],[745,\"Collected payments only, with tips\"],[266,\"Column\"],[461,\"Column\"],[471,\"Column\"],[355,\"Combined revenue across all staff\"],[326,\"Commission\"],[557,\"Commission\"],[330,\"Commission Calculations\"],[425,\"Commission Calculations\"],[516,\"Commission Calculations\"],[383,\"Commission from product sales\"],[379,\"Commission from voucher sales\"],[335,\"Commission is only accessible to admin users.\"],[400,\"Commission rules\"],[144,\"Completed\"],[183,\"Completing the payment\"],[889,\"Components\"],[890,\"Components\"],[755,\"Configure your branches, business hours, payment methods, and permissions\"],[775,\"Contact email and phone\"],[899,\"Contact Us\"],[888,\"Controls whether they appear in client-facing booking\"],[177,\"Count your physical stock and spot any discrepancies\"],[143,\"Counting is done — ready to review and confirm\"],[132,\"Create a **voucher code** — this is what the client enters at checkout.\"],[325,\"Create a client directly from the Calendar while booking\"],[276,\"Created at\"],[99,\"Creating a membership\"],[101,\"Creating a voucher\"],[198,\"Credit or debit card\"],[633,\"CSV\"],[598,\"Custom folders you create to organise reports\"],[644,\"Custom start and end date\"],[234,\"Customer name and phone\"],[927,\"Customise how your booking page looks to clients.\"],[647,\"Daily Sales\"],[738,\"Daily Sales\"],[414,\"Dashboard\"],[539,\"Dashboard\"],[426,\"Dashboard Overview\"],[593,\"Dashboards\"],[81,\"Date navigation\"],[296,\"Date of birth (can be added here if not set)\"],[706,\"Date of birth (optional)\"],[498,\"Date range filter\"],[577,\"Date range options\"],[778,\"Date the branch was created\"],[297,\"Date the client was added to the system\"],[707,\"Date the client was created in the system\"],[611,\"Day\"],[393,\"Deduction\"],[799,\"Default hours are **08:00 AM – 11:45 PM**.\"],[809,\"Deleting a payment method is permanent. If you just want to stop it appearing at checkout temporarily, edit it and set it to inactive instead.\"],[196,\"Description\"],[373,\"Description\"],[315,\"Details\"],[399,\"Details\"],[872,\"Details\"],[250,\"Discount, tip, split payment, or voucher\"],[672,\"Discounts show in red when applied. Search by client name or service, or filter by date range. Click **Export** to download as CSV.\"],[206,\"Divide the bill across more than one payment method\"],[222,\"Divide the total across multiple payment methods\"],[409,\"Download the full calculations for payroll\"],[835,\"Each card has three action buttons:\"],[858,\"Each card shows the user's name, their **Auth User** label, email address, and Location ID.\"],[804,\"Each method is shown as a card with its name, **Active** status badge, and the date it was created.\"],[390,\"Each row has editable fields for rate, days, and hours. The **Total Earning** is calculated automatically.\"],[852,\"Each staff member can have their own weekly schedule so the Calendar only shows them as available when they're actually working.\"],[372,\"Earning\"],[558,\"Earnings and salary slips\"],[897,\"Edit your profile\"],[757,\"Editing a branch\"],[826,\"Editing a team member\"],[9,\"Editing an appointment\"],[762,\"Editing or deleting a payment method\"],[95,\"Editing or removing a service\"],[920,\"Email Address\"],[387,\"End of service accrual\"],[739,\"End-of-day reconciliation — cash, card, and tips totals\"],[392,\"Enter any amounts to deduct:\"],[343,\"Enter the **Default rate** — the percentage they'll earn (e.g., 30%).\"],[117,\"Enter the product's **name**, **brand**, **category**, and **supplier**.\"],[861,\"Enter their **Email** (required) — this will be their username when logging in.\"],[842,\"Enter their **First Name** (required) and **Last Name**.\"],[386,\"EOS\"],[682,\"Every payment transaction that was successfully collected — similar to Sales Transactions but focused on the payment side only. Voided sales are excluded here.\"],[590,\"Every report in one place\"],[121,\"Every time a product is sold at checkout, your stock count goes down automatically. Use the Stock Audit tab when you want to check your physical stock against what the system shows.\"],[697,\"Every tip that's been collected, attributed to the staff member who received it.\"],[519,\"Everything you need to run your salon — bookings, payments, staff, and more\"],[635,\"Excel (.xlsx)\"],[408,\"Export CSV\"],[576,\"Export options\"],[591,\"Favourites\"],[77,\"Feature\"],[314,\"Feature\"],[398,\"Feature\"],[871,\"Feature\"],[914,\"Field\"],[928,\"Field\"],[781,\"Fields you can update:\"],[281,\"Fill in the client's details:\"],[495,\"Filter by month and year using the dropdowns at the top of the widget. The date range being shown is displayed at the bottom of the table.\"],[416,\"Filtering by Date Range\"],[573,\"Finance Summary\"],[561,\"Financial reports and analytics\"],[569,\"Finding a report\"],[521,\"Finding your way around\"],[319,\"First name, phone required — email, DOB, notes, location optional\"],[597,\"Folders\"],[239,\"For **Thermal Receipt**, you can **Download PDF** or **Browser Print**.\\r\\nFor **Standard Invoice**, click **Print**.\"],[795,\"For each day of the week (Sunday through Saturday), you can:\"],[854,\"For each day of the week, set their **start** and **finish time**.\"],[631,\"Format\"],[162,\"From here you can:\"],[227,\"From here you can:\"],[240,\"From the sale receipt screen you can navigate directly to the client's full profile to see their history, memberships, and vouchers.\"],[411,\"Full payroll advice with earnings, deductions, and net salary — downloadable as XLS\"],[322,\"Full profile\"],[743,\"Full transaction log including voided sales\"],[480,\"Generate a salary slip for that team member\"],[749,\"Gift card purchases and redemptions\"],[175,\"Gift cards and discount codes\"],[124,\"Give the membership a **name** and choose which **service** it applies to.\"],[111,\"Give the service a **name**, choose a **category** (e.g., Hair, Nails), set the **duration** in minutes, and enter the **price**.\"],[131,\"Give the voucher a **name** and choose the discount type: a **fixed amount** (e.g., AED 100 off) or a **percentage** (e.g., 20% off).\"],[123,\"Go to **Catalog → Memberships** and click **Add Membership**.\"],[116,\"Go to **Catalog → Products** and click **Add Product**.\"],[110,\"Go to **Catalog → Services** and click **Add Service**.\"],[146,\"Go to **Catalog → Stock Audit** and click **Start New Audit Session**.\"],[130,\"Go to **Catalog → Vouchers** and click **Add Voucher**.\"],[12,\"Going to checkout from the calendar\"],[886,\"Grants full access to Reports, Settings, Commission, and Dashboard\"],[753,\"Gratuity records by staff member\"],[90,\"Hover an appointment to see a quick summary without opening it\"],[89,\"Hover card\"],[36,\"Hover over any appointment card on the calendar to see a quick summary popup showing:\"],[78,\"How it works\"],[448,\"How many are **confirmed**\"],[449,\"How many have been **cancelled**\"],[466,\"How many times it was booked this month\"],[503,\"How revenue was collected (cash, card, online, etc.)\"],[3,\"How the Calendar is laid out\"],[900,\"How the client booking flow works\"],[237,\"How the sale was paid\"],[241,\"If a mistake was made, click the **Void Sale** button (shown in red on the right side of the receipt screen). This will cancel the transaction and reverse the sale record.\"],[867,\"If someone leaves but you want to keep their history in the system, archive them instead of deleting.\"],[634,\"Importing into a spreadsheet\"],[140,\"In Progress\"],[191,\"In the **Edit Appointment** panel that opens, click the **Checkout** button at the bottom right.\"],[273,\"Internal reviews added by your team\"],[233,\"Invoice number, date, time, and receptionist\"],[874,\"JPEG or PNG, max 2 MB\"],[934,\"Landing Page Image\"],[620,\"Last 3 years\"],[612,\"Last 30 days, one column per day\"],[618,\"Last 4 quarters\"],[614,\"Last 4 weeks\"],[616,\"Last 6 months (default)\"],[505,\"Last 7 days revenue with a daily trend chart\"],[641,\"Last 7, 30, or 90 days\"],[467,\"Last month\"],[477,\"Last month\"],[468,\"Last month's count for comparison\"],[478,\"Last month's total for comparison\"],[642,\"Last week / Last month / Last 3, 6, or 12 months\"],[509,\"Live feed of the latest appointment events\"],[407,\"Live monthly breakdown per staff member\"],[773,\"Location ID\"],[930,\"Logo Text\"],[741,\"Looking up a specific service or client visit\"],[311,\"Loyalty\"],[721,\"Loyalty\"],[312,\"Loyalty programme activity\"],[722,\"Loyalty programme activity\"],[112,\"Make sure the status is set to **Active** — only active services show up when booking.\"],[876,\"Makes each staff member's column easy to identify\"],[258,\"Manage your client database — add, search, and view full client profiles\"],[896,\"Manage your public booking Module and salon website profile\"],[855,\"Mark any day as **Off** if they don't work that day.\"],[46,\"Marks the client as checked in and present\"],[48,\"Marks the service as actively in progress\"],[98,\"Memberships\"],[172,\"Memberships\"],[309,\"Memberships\"],[651,\"Memberships\"],[719,\"Memberships\"],[746,\"Memberships\"],[122,\"Memberships are prepaid session packages — a client pays upfront for a bundle of appointments (for example, 10 haircuts for the price of 8). Each time they come in and use a session, it's deducted from their balance automatically.\"],[270,\"Mobile number\"],[918,\"Mobile Number\"],[615,\"Month\"],[517,\"Monthly commission summary per staff member\"],[513,\"Most booked services this month vs. last\"],[85,\"Multiple services\"],[269,\"Name with an avatar (initials if no photo)\"],[293,\"Name, phone, and email\"],[703,\"Name, phone, and email\"],[499,\"Narrow all dashboard data to any period\"],[69,\"Need to mark a staff member as unavailable for a break, training, or any other reason? You can block out time without creating a real appointment.\"],[507,\"Next 7 days bookings — confirmed vs. cancelled\"],[404,\"No Setup badge\"],[65,\"No Show\"],[157,\"Not sure which to pick? If you didn't actually check those products, choose **Sync counted to previous stock** — that way only the items you physically counted will be updated.\"],[774,\"Number of staff assigned\"],[353,\"Number of staff with sales in this period\"],[907,\"NxCut automatically creates a public booking Module for your salon. Clients can visit it to browse your services, pick a staff member, choose a time, and book an appointment — without you needing to do anything to set it up.\"],[190,\"On the Calendar, click on the appointment card you want to check out.\"],[30,\"On the right side of the panel, click **+ Add service**. A service picker will open showing all your available services with their price and duration.\"],[128,\"Once a client buys a membership at checkout, their session count is tracked automatically on their client profile. Sessions are used up each time they check out using that membership.\"],[73,\"Once a client's appointment is done, you can take payment directly from the calendar.\"],[158,\"Once all items are counted and saved, the audit moves to **Review** status. On this page you'll see:\"],[397,\"Once the slip is complete, click **Download XLS** to save it as a spreadsheet, or **Close** to exit without saving.\"],[165,\"Once you click **Complete**, the audit is finalised and cannot be edited. Make sure everything looks right before confirming.\"],[29,\"Once you select a client, their name, phone, and email will be confirmed on screen. You can click **Change Client** if you need to swap to someone else, or **View \\\\[Client]'s Profile** to open their full history.\"],[800,\"Once you've made your changes, click **Save Global Hours**. To reset all days back to the defaults at once, click **Reset to Default**.\"],[225,\"Once you've selected the payment method and applied any discounts or tips, click the &#x2A;*Pay AED \\\\[amount]** button at the bottom right to finalise the sale.\"],[80,\"One column per team member with their photo\"],[204,\"Online payment\"],[868,\"Open their profile and choose **Archive**.\"],[195,\"Option\"],[215,\"Option\"],[878,\"Optional internal staff ID number\"],[863,\"Optionally enter a **Display Name** and **Phone Number**.\"],[844,\"Optionally enter a **Team Member ID** — useful if your business uses internal staff ID numbers.\"],[133,\"Optionally set an **expiry date** and a **usage limit** (e.g., can only be used once).\"],[126,\"Optionally set an **expiry period** — for example, all sessions must be used within 12 months of purchase.\"],[376,\"Over Time\"],[377,\"Overtime hours worked\"],[922,\"Owner Name\"],[200,\"Pay with cash\"],[418,\"Payment Methods\"],[502,\"Payment Methods\"],[760,\"Payment Methods\"],[574,\"Payment Transactions\"],[650,\"Payments\"],[744,\"Payments\"],[637,\"PDF\"],[880,\"Per-category toggles — controls which services they can be booked for\"],[571,\"Performance Dashboard\"],[609,\"Period\"],[763,\"Permissions\"],[811,\"Permissions let you control the rules around tips and discounts at checkout. Settings are per location — select the location you want to configure from the **Location** dropdown at the top.\"],[595,\"Premium\"],[596,\"Premium-tier reports\"],[173,\"Prepaid session bundles for specific services\"],[766,\"Prevent Tips with Manual Discount\"],[403,\"Preview the commission payout before saving\"],[253,\"Print receipt\"],[185,\"Print the receipt\"],[638,\"Printing or sharing outside the system\"],[96,\"Products\"],[170,\"Products\"],[305,\"Products\"],[382,\"Products\"],[653,\"Products\"],[715,\"Products\"],[750,\"Products\"],[115,\"Products are the retail or consumable items you sell or use in your salon — shampoos, styling products, skincare, and so on. NxCut tracks your stock levels automatically as products are sold.\"],[306,\"Products purchased by this client\"],[716,\"Products purchased by this client\"],[873,\"Profile photo\"],[617,\"Quarter\"],[324,\"Quick add\"],[13,\"Quick reference\"],[262,\"Quick reference\"],[332,\"Quick reference\"],[657,\"Quick reference\"],[831,\"Quick reference\"],[419,\"Recent Sales\"],[504,\"Recent Sales\"],[50,\"Records that the client didn't show up\"],[202,\"Redeem a pre-paid session from the client's membership\"],[224,\"Redeem a voucher code to reduce the balance\"],[567,\"Reporting & Analytics\"],[560,\"Reports\"],[580,\"Reports are only accessible to admin users.\"],[592,\"Reports you've starred for quick access\"],[171,\"Retail and consumable items, with automatic stock tracking\"],[751,\"Retail sales with live stock levels\"],[501,\"Revenue breakdown by branch\"],[142,\"Review\"],[272,\"Reviews\"],[410,\"Salary slip\"],[331,\"Salary Slip\"],[656,\"Sale Details\"],[252,\"Sale is recorded and receipt screen appears\"],[184,\"Sale receipt\"],[274,\"Sales\"],[303,\"Sales\"],[545,\"Sales\"],[713,\"Sales\"],[417,\"Sales by Location\"],[500,\"Sales by Location\"],[546,\"Sales history and transactions\"],[645,\"Sales Hub\"],[572,\"Sales Log\"],[320,\"Sales total\"],[649,\"Sales Transactions\"],[742,\"Sales Transactions\"],[916,\"Salon Name\"],[402,\"Sample calculator\"],[150,\"Scan the same product multiple times to keep adding to its count — each scan increments the quantity by 1.\"],[59,\"Scheduled\"],[316,\"Search\"],[695,\"Search by product name, SKU, barcode, or category.\"],[699,\"Search by staff name, payment method, or sale ID. Filter by date range.\"],[496,\"Section\"],[536,\"Section\"],[736,\"Section\"],[84,\"Select \\\"Walk-In Customer\\\" — no profile needed\"],[848,\"Select a **Location** (required).\"],[865,\"Select a **Location** (required).\"],[339,\"Select a **Team Member** from the dropdown.\"],[25,\"Select an **existing client** from the list\"],[147,\"Select the products you want to include in this count.\"],[884,\"Separate login accounts shown with an orange border\"],[463,\"Service\"],[93,\"Services\"],[168,\"Services\"],[940,\"Services are grouped by category (Facial, Hair, Nails, etc.). Prices include 5% VAT. The client taps a category to see the individual services and their prices, then selects the one they want.\"],[109,\"Services are the treatments your team performs — haircuts, color, manicures, massages, and so on. Every service you add here will be available to select when booking an appointment.\"],[235,\"Services performed and the staff team\"],[728,\"Services performed with time, duration, and assigned team\"],[552,\"Services, products, and packages\"],[747,\"Session usage and package status\"],[845,\"Set **Category Permissions** — toggle on the service categories this staff member is allowed to perform (e.g., Hair, Nails, Facial). All categories are enabled by default. Staff will only appear as a booking option for the categories you enable.\"],[843,\"Set a **Calendar Color** — this is the color used for their column on the Calendar. Each staff member should have a distinct color to make them easy to tell apart.\"],[862,\"Set a **Password** (required).\"],[796,\"Set a **Start Time** and **End Time**\"],[401,\"Set per staff member with a fixed rate and sales period\"],[882,\"Set per staff member, per day of the week\"],[118,\"Set the **price** and enter your current **stock quantity**.\"],[344,\"Set the **Sales period** — how often commission is calculated. The default is **Monthly**. NxCut will show you exactly when the first and following periods will be.\"],[125,\"Set the number of **sessions** included and the total **price**.\"],[71,\"Set the start time, end time, and an optional note so the team knows why the slot is blocked.\"],[327,\"Set up commission rules for your staff and generate detailed salary slips\"],[92,\"Set up your services, products, memberships, vouchers, and manage stock\"],[329,\"Setting up a commission rule\"],[827,\"Setting working hours (Edit Shift)\"],[759,\"Setting your hours\"],[563,\"Settings\"],[754,\"Settings\"],[768,\"Settings is only accessible to admin users.\"],[767,\"Settings is where you control the core configuration of your salon. Click **Settings** in the left menu to get started. There are four sections: **Branches**, **Calendar**, **Payment Methods**, and **Permissions**.\"],[321,\"Shown directly in the client list\"],[79,\"Staff columns\"],[405,\"Staff member has sales but no commission rule configured\"],[474,\"Staff member's name\"],[555,\"Staff profiles and schedules\"],[599,\"Star any report card to add it to your **Favourites**.\"],[63,\"Start\"],[180,\"Starting a checkout\"],[57,\"Status\"],[138,\"Status\"],[243,\"Step\"],[5,\"Step 1 — Select a client\"],[901,\"Step 1 — Select a location\"],[103,\"Step 1 — Stock Session\"],[6,\"Step 2 — Add services\"],[902,\"Step 2 — Browse the price menu\"],[104,\"Step 2 — Stock Entry (Counting)\"],[903,\"Step 3 — Pick a professional\"],[7,\"Step 3 — Save\"],[105,\"Step 3 — Stock Review\"],[904,\"Step 4 — Choose a date and time\"],[905,\"Step 5 — Enter contact details\"],[906,\"Step 6 — Appointment confirmed\"],[102,\"Stock Audit\"],[176,\"Stock Audit\"],[210,\"Subtotal (after any discount)\"],[236,\"Subtotal, VAT (5%), and total\"],[730,\"Subtotal, VAT (5%), and Total\"],[166,\"Tab\"],[299,\"Tab\"],[709,\"Tab\"],[388,\"Target\"],[389,\"Target-based incentives\"],[554,\"Team\"],[822,\"Team Management\"],[473,\"Team member\"],[328,\"Team Member Commissions\"],[877,\"Team Member ID\"],[352,\"Team Members\"],[824,\"Team Members\"],[834,\"Team Members are the staff profiles that appear on the Calendar. Each card shows the staff member's photo (or initials if no photo is set), their email, and phone number.\"],[21,\"The **+ Add** button in the top right corner is for selling products, memberships, or vouchers directly — it opens a cart where you select the items and a client. It is **not** for creating appointments. To book an appointment, click directly on an empty time slot in a staff column.\"],[481,\"The **Actions** column has a salary slip icon — click it to open a formatted breakdown of that person's services, commission, and total payout for the period.\"],[857,\"The **Authenticated Users** section sits below the team member grid and shows all staff login accounts. These cards have an **orange border** to distinguish them from team member profiles.\"],[694,\"The **Current Stock** column shows a warning icon (⚠) when stock is running low. The **Status** badge will show **Low Stock** to flag items that need reordering.\"],[790,\"The **Location ID** is shown at the top of the form but cannot be edited — it's a system-generated identifier.\"],[161,\"The **price difference** — the value impact of any discrepancies\"],[160,\"The **quantity difference** between what the system expected and what you physically counted\"],[340,\"The **Services Commission** section is enabled by default. This means the staff member earns commission on the services they perform.\"],[676,\"The **Status** column shows either:\"],[688,\"The **Status** shows either **Active** (sessions still available) or **Completed** (all sessions used). The progress bar makes it easy to see at a glance how far through a package a client is.\"],[396,\"The **Total Deduction** and final **Net Salary** are calculated automatically at the bottom.\"],[60,\"The appointment is booked and upcoming\"],[954,\"The appointment is instantly added to your Calendar in NxCut and visible to the assigned staff member.\"],[454,\"The appointment time\"],[68,\"The appointment was cancelled\"],[145,\"The audit is finalised and can no longer be edited\"],[141,\"The audit is open and items are being counted\"],[770,\"The Branches page shows all your salon locations. Each branch is displayed as a card showing:\"],[14,\"The Calendar is where all your appointments live. It shows your team's full schedule side by side — one column per staff member — so you can see everyone's day at a glance and book new appointments in seconds.\"],[107,\"The Catalog is where you define everything your salon offers — the services your team performs, the products you sell, membership packages, gift vouchers, and your product inventory. Think of it as the foundation that powers your bookings and checkout.\"],[181,\"The checkout screen\"],[193,\"The checkout screen is split into two areas:\"],[192,\"The checkout screen slides in from the right, showing the client's name and the services from the appointment already loaded.\"],[213,\"The chosen payment method and amount\"],[941,\"The client chooses which staff member they'd like. They can pick a specific person or select **Any Agent** to be assigned to whoever is available.\"],[66,\"The client didn't show up\"],[944,\"The client fills in their information:\"],[62,\"The client has arrived at the salon\"],[259,\"The client list\"],[263,\"The Client List is your salon's client database. Every person who visits your salon can have a profile here, making it easy to look them up, track their history, and manage their memberships and vouchers.\"],[939,\"The client picks which branch they want to visit. If you only have one location, this step is skipped automatically.\"],[456,\"The client's name (or Walk-In)\"],[39,\"The client's name and phone number\"],[333,\"The Commission page is where you define how much each staff member earns from the services they perform, and view a live breakdown of what they've earned. NxCut calculates everything automatically based on real sales data.\"],[38,\"The current status badge (e.g., **Scheduled**)\"],[428,\"The Dashboard is only visible to admin users.\"],[427,\"The Dashboard is the first thing you see when you log in as an admin. It gives you a quick, up-to-date picture of how your salon is performing — without having to dig through reports or spreadsheets.\"],[951,\"The date, time, service, agent, and location\"],[801,\"The end time must always be later than the start time. Invalid entries will not be saved.\"],[432,\"The entire Dashboard updates automatically to reflect only that period.\"],[913,\"The first section lets you update your salon's basic public information.\"],[935,\"The hero image at the top of your booking page (PNG, JPG, GIF or WebP, max 5MB)\"],[794,\"The hours are configured per location. You'll see \\\"Configuring for: \\\\[location name]\\\" at the top so you always know which branch you're editing.\"],[23,\"The left side of the panel shows your client list. You can:\"],[586,\"The left sidebar organises reports into:\"],[279,\"The list is paginated — use the **Previous / Next** buttons at the bottom to navigate, and adjust the **Show** dropdown to control how many results appear per page.\"],[581,\"The main reports page shows all available reports as cards. You can:\"],[265,\"The main view shows a table of all your clients with the following columns:\"],[917,\"The name displayed on your booking page\"],[923,\"The name of the salon owner\"],[464,\"The name of the treatment\"],[661,\"The page is split into three parts:\"],[336,\"The page is split into two sections: **Team Member Commissions** (your commission rules) and **Commission Calculations** (the live earnings breakdown).\"],[933,\"The page title shown in the browser tab\"],[76,\"The payment screen opens with the services already loaded. Follow the Checkout steps to apply discounts, add a tip, and collect payment.\"],[701,\"The profile is split into two parts:\"],[578,\"The Reports section gives you a deeper look at your salon's performance beyond the day-to-day. All reports are filterable, exportable, and organised by category so you can find what you need quickly.\"],[658,\"The Sales Hub is your complete record of everything that's been sold or paid for. Click **Sales** in the left menu and you'll see a sidebar with eight sections. Each one is focused on a different part of your business and has its own search, date filter, and **Export** button.\"],[347,\"The sample calculation updates in real time as you type — use it to make sure the numbers look right before saving.\"],[34,\"The selected services appear in the **Appointment** panel showing the time, duration, assigned team, and price. The total updates automatically at the bottom.\"],[455,\"The service being performed\"],[64,\"The service is currently in progress\"],[40,\"The service name, team, duration, and price\"],[369,\"The slip is headed with your salon's name and labelled as **Payroll Advice**. It shows the staff member's name, their occupancy percentage, free hours, the month, and their title.\"],[457,\"The staff member handling it\"],[458,\"The status badge (e.g., **Booked**)\"],[53,\"The status is reflected both on the appointment card and in the hover popup.\"],[360,\"The table below shows each staff member with:\"],[832,\"The Team Management page is where you manage everyone who works at your salon — their profiles, working hours, service permissions, and login accounts.\"],[931,\"The text displayed as your logo\"],[37,\"The time range (e.g., 14:30 – 15:30)\"],[169,\"The treatments your team performs\"],[909,\"The Website section is only accessible to admin users.\"],[493,\"Their commission rate and calculated amount\"],[492,\"Their commission type (or **No Setup** if commission hasn't been configured yet)\"],[375,\"Their fixed monthly salary\"],[490,\"Their number of sales\"],[271,\"Their phone number\"],[491,\"Their total sales value\"],[812,\"There are three permission settings:\"],[947,\"They can also add any **special requests or notes** in the Additional Comments field.\"],[436,\"This gives you an instant feel for which branches are driving the most revenue — especially useful if you run multiple locations.\"],[523,\"This guide walks you through every part of NxCut in plain, simple language. No technical experience needed.\"],[149,\"This is where you physically count your stock. The entry screen opens in **barcode mode** by default — just scan a product's barcode and NxCut will find it automatically and add 1 to its counted quantity. Each scan is saved instantly, so you don't need to do anything extra.\"],[793,\"This is where you set your salon's **Global Working Hours** — the default opening and closing times that appear on the Calendar for all staff.\"],[452,\"This is your go-to for staying on top of last-minute changes, especially if you're managing more than one location.\"],[465,\"This month\"],[475,\"This month\"],[803,\"This page shows all the payment options available at checkout. The default methods are: **Card**, **Cash**, **Membership**, **Online**, **Split Payment**, and **Voucher** — all active by default.\"],[337,\"This section lists all the commission rules you've set up. If no rules have been created yet, it will show \\\"No commission settings found — add a commission setting to get started.\\\"\"],[937,\"This section shows the contact details displayed to clients on your booking page — your email address and WhatsApp number. These are pulled from your profile automatically.\"],[86,\"Tick as many services as needed in the service picker\"],[31,\"Tick the **checkbox** next to any service you want to add\"],[797,\"Tick the **Closed** checkbox if the salon is closed that day — it will be hidden from the Calendar entirely\"],[654,\"Tips\"],[752,\"Tips\"],[684,\"Tips show in the Tips column when they were added to the sale. Search by client name or sale ID, or filter by date range.\"],[575,\"Tips Summary\"],[791,\"To add a new branch, contact NxCut support. Branch creation is managed at the account level and cannot be done directly from this page.\"],[22,\"To create an appointment, click on any **empty time slot** in a staff member's column. A booking panel will slide open on the right side of the screen.\"],[839,\"To view archived staff, toggle **Show archived team members only** in the top right corner.\"],[640,\"Today / Yesterday\"],[422,\"Today's Next Appointments\"],[510,\"Today's Next Appointments\"],[847,\"Toggle **Admin User** on if they need full access to the system (Reports, Settings, Commission, Dashboard). Off by default.\"],[864,\"Toggle **Admin User** on if they should have full system access.\"],[870,\"Toggle **Show archived team members only** at the top of the page to find them again.\"],[846,\"Toggle **Visible to Clients** on if this staff member should appear in client-facing booking. This is on by default.\"],[119,\"Toggle it to **Active** so it's available to add during checkout.\"],[515,\"Top earners with salary slip and export\"],[423,\"Top Services\"],[512,\"Top Services\"],[424,\"Top Team Members\"],[514,\"Top Team Members\"],[209,\"Total amount (excluding discounts)\"],[275,\"Total amount spent across all visits\"],[447,\"Total appointments booked\"],[356,\"Total Commission\"],[357,\"Total commission owed to the team\"],[354,\"Total Sales\"],[476,\"Total sales value for the current month\"],[777,\"TRN (Tax Registration Number)\"],[420,\"Upcoming Appointments\"],[506,\"Upcoming Appointments\"],[345,\"Use the **Sample calculation** box to double-check your setup. Enter a sale amount and NxCut will show you the exact commission calculation — including the threshold, commissionable amount, and final payout.\"],[278,\"Use the **search bar** at the top to find anyone by name, email, or phone number.\"],[434,\"Use the &#x2A;*\\\\<*&#x2A; and &#x2A;*>** arrows on the calendar to navigate to earlier or later months.\"],[459,\"Use this for a quick check of what's still to come in the day.\"],[82,\"Use Today, \\\\<, and > buttons to change the day\"],[211,\"VAT (5%)\"],[186,\"View the client's profile\"],[646,\"View, filter, and export your full sales history — appointments, payments, memberships, vouchers, products, and tips\"],[261,\"Viewing a client's profile\"],[887,\"Visible to clients\"],[594,\"Visual overview reports (e.g. Performance dashboard)\"],[187,\"Void a sale\"],[255,\"Void Sale\"],[735,\"Voiding a sale cannot be undone. Only use this if there was a genuine error with the transaction.\"],[242,\"Voiding a sale cannot be undone. Only void a sale if you're certain there was an error — for example, the wrong client was charged or the wrong services were added.\"],[378,\"Voucher\"],[100,\"Vouchers\"],[174,\"Vouchers\"],[307,\"Vouchers\"],[652,\"Vouchers\"],[717,\"Vouchers\"],[748,\"Vouchers\"],[129,\"Vouchers are gift cards or discount codes that clients can redeem when paying for services or products. You set the value (either a fixed amount or a percentage off), and NxCut tracks how much has been used and what's left.\"],[718,\"Vouchers associated with this client\"],[308,\"Vouchers linked to this client\"],[83,\"Walk-in booking\"],[924,\"Website\"],[895,\"Website & Booking Module\"],[898,\"Website Details\"],[932,\"Website Title\"],[613,\"Week\"],[643,\"Week-to-date / Month-to-date / Quarter-to-date / Year-to-date\"],[522,\"Welcome to **NxCut** — your all-in-one salon management system. Whether you're booking an appointment, collecting payment, managing your team, or checking how your business is doing, everything you need is right here.\"],[518,\"Welcome to NxCut\"],[520,\"What can NxCut do for you?\"],[244,\"What happens\"],[44,\"What it does\"],[216,\"What it does\"],[58,\"What it means\"],[139,\"What it means\"],[267,\"What it shows\"],[300,\"What it shows\"],[351,\"What it shows\"],[462,\"What it shows\"],[472,\"What it shows\"],[710,\"What it shows\"],[497,\"What it tells you\"],[167,\"What it's for\"],[537,\"What it's for\"],[915,\"What it's for\"],[929,\"What it's for\"],[610,\"What you'll see\"],[588,\"What's in it\"],[511,\"What's still happening today\"],[938,\"When a client visits your booking page, they go through a simple step-by-step process:\"],[277,\"When the client was added to the system\"],[820,\"When turned on, a staff member cannot apply both a manual discount and a tip to the same sale. If a discount is applied, the tip option is disabled — and vice versa.\"],[814,\"When turned on, clients can use a voucher as the payment method when adding a tip at checkout.\"],[817,\"When turned on, the ability to add tips is completely removed from the POS checkout screen. Tips would only be accepted through online bookings.\"],[535,\"When you log in, you'll see a menu on the left side of the screen. Each item takes you to a different part of NxCut.\"],[15,\"When you open the Calendar you'll see:\"],[538,\"Who can see it\"],[881,\"Working hours\"],[619,\"Year\"],[290,\"You can also add a client on the spot while booking an appointment in the Calendar — no need to come here first.\"],[482,\"You can also export the full table using the **CSV**, **Excel**, or **PDF** buttons in the top-right corner.\"],[135,\"You can check a client's remaining voucher balance and full usage history on their profile under Clients → Voucher Activity.\"],[32,\"You can select multiple services at once\"],[851,\"You cannot remove admin access from the last remaining admin. Make sure at least one other admin exists before making that change.\"],[28,\"You don't need to pre-register a client. Walk-In Customer works perfectly for first-time or unregistered visitors.\"],[925,\"Your auto-generated booking URL (read-only)\"],[674,\"Your complete transaction history across all sale types. By default it shows the last 30 days.\"],[921,\"Your contact email\"],[660,\"Your end-of-day summary. Use the **Today*&#x2A;, &#x2A;*\\\\<*&#x2A;, and &#x2A;*>** buttons to pick any day and see a full breakdown of what happened.\"],[232,\"Your salon name, TRN, and branch location\"],[919,\"Your salon's contact number\"]],\"type\":\"string\"},\"page_id\":{\"docs\":{\"1\":49,\"2\":50,\"3\":51,\"4\":52,\"5\":53,\"6\":54,\"7\":55,\"8\":56,\"9\":57,\"10\":58,\"11\":59,\"12\":60,\"13\":61,\"14\":62,\"15\":63,\"16\":64,\"17\":65,\"18\":66,\"19\":67,\"20\":68,\"21\":69,\"22\":70,\"23\":71,\"24\":72,\"25\":73,\"26\":74,\"27\":75,\"28\":76,\"29\":77,\"30\":78,\"31\":79,\"32\":80,\"33\":81,\"34\":82,\"35\":83,\"36\":84,\"37\":85,\"38\":86,\"39\":87,\"40\":88,\"41\":89,\"42\":90,\"43\":91,\"44\":92,\"45\":93,\"46\":94,\"47\":95,\"48\":96,\"49\":97,\"50\":98,\"51\":99,\"52\":100,\"53\":101,\"54\":102,\"55\":103,\"56\":104,\"57\":105,\"58\":106,\"59\":107,\"60\":108,\"61\":109,\"62\":110,\"63\":111,\"64\":112,\"65\":113,\"66\":114,\"67\":115,\"68\":116,\"69\":117,\"70\":118,\"71\":119,\"72\":120,\"73\":121,\"74\":122,\"75\":123,\"76\":124,\"77\":125,\"78\":126,\"79\":127,\"80\":128,\"81\":129,\"82\":1